      "content": "The weight of feeling completely out of control is immense, and it makes the idea of taking charge feel like the only logical option. If the body feels like a prison, the thought of finding a way to end the discomfort can feel like the ultimate act of self-determination. Please know that there are people who can help you navigate these feelings without judgment; a professional can offer strategies for managing this profound sense of hopelessness. If you are in immediate danger, please contact emergency services.",
